CUI notes

desired information for each device:

last_seen
name
address
vendor if classic or le public
company if le random
classic_rssi || le_rssi
extra if populated: classic_minor_class, appearance, company_type (company if company_type = Unknown (12))

last_seen will be a decay flag like in kismet.  ! for within 5 seconds . for within 45 seconds, ? for longer than 45 seconds but still online (offline 
devices are not shown)
